5872a6ee763f8139e9","tid":848874,"uid":37358,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T09:25:35.000Z","msg":"咁嘅質素想單靠民主光環選到？收皮啦<br />\n<br />\n屌麗老師文宣冇！（平凡的幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n政績冇!（乜撚嘢免供全民退保會行得通？我屌你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n最叻就係話馮檢基𠝹票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正一垃圾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T09:51:05.000Z","msg":"佢點解會咁驚馮檢基出嚟選？<br />\n就係因為佢無樣嘢得，<br />\n廢到馮檢基都𠝹得走佢啲票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T10:51:18.000Z","msg":"泛民就係咁濕鳩，佢地如果走去齊齊撐哥基，以佢嘅人氣同喺深水埗嘅地區工作，一定贏硬健康大使。不過，泛民剩係識撐自己友，叫佢地顧全大局唔駛諗"},{"pid":"076d673a19031681db26f0be7f4455f1c0684da9","tid":848874,"uid":93784,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ac994597e5119340b42c130d5e2fa6182d6168cd","tid":848874,"uid":70301,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T09:44:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真 有時見香港人仲用緊咩「呀爺」「保皇黨」「內地」難聽過粗口</blockquote><br />\n保皇黨有咩問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得建制派難聽好多喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n建制建制，講到佢哋好似建設緊個制度咁，其他人就好似淨係識破壞咁<br />\n<br />\n建制派重難聽過保皇黨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:21:27.000Z","msg":"叫佢地親中派 共狗 共奴 就啱架啦<br />\n<br />\n佢地所作所為只係助紂為虐 損害制度 談不上保皇<br />\n<br />\n人地保皇黨真係為國家好 為國王好 高尚好多<br />\n<br />\n呢班賤種配唔起呢個名喎<br />\n<br />\n我都記得香港「建制派」同真正建制係唔同意思 <br />\n<br />\n其實香港人都係慣左用建制/保皇去形容佢地依附政權(中共)為政權服務<br />\n<br />\n但建制/保皇都唔太正確去形容香港呢班賤種<br />\n<br />\n仲有「非建制派」又係ON9 仲要係泛民自甘墜落去用 <br />\n<br />\n你不如叫對家做「非民主派」啦 點會叫自己做「非建制派」<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解傳媒走去用呢個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a4a7e5a5d567ec46d9a44315b77be1232a3276","tid":848874,"uid":11809,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:52:41.000Z","msg":"一定投小麗"},{"pid":"e1dc1b418612dfa40e23785ee246282ab2e13093","tid":848874,"uid":45352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:55:28.000Z","msg":"咩年代，仲阿爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b038aa745d994660ed606f4d076ba04f07a17ace","tid":848874,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acfa28df02772f494c1545f746cf5db022683ee8","tid":848874,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1dc1b418612dfa40e23785ee246282ab2e13093","tid":848874,"uid":45352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:55:28.000Z","msg":"咩年代，仲阿爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:34:55.000Z","msg":"無計,佢俾劉細亮果班老廢柴日日播毒<br />\n以為聽條廢柴講就有9萬6"},{"pid":"aee909c245318e56500a8949561e55b56cd3c31d","tid":848874,"uid":91317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:46:38.000Z","msg":"硬係有浸柒味"},{"pid":"7a78134e69056f14786f63eddd5adf2108131f05","tid":848874,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:59:43.000Z","msg":"劉小麗為9萬6講嘢"}]}